\date{2024-06-18}
\title{pointwise Kan extensions are computed by (co)limit formulae}
\taxon{proposition}
\author{rileyshahar}

\import{macros01}
\cite{riehl-2017}{Riehl}{Theorem 6.3.7}

\p{A [Kan extension](rs-0051) with [locally small](rs-002Q) codomains is
[pointwise](rs-0067) if and only if it is computed by the [(co)limit
formula](rs-0065) of the appropriate variance.}

